---
title: Korma Spiced Pea and Potato Cakes with Baby Plum Tomato Salad and Coriander Yoghurt
description: Making potato cakes are easier than you think! Flavoured with warming korma curry paste and studded with peas, these are paired with mango chutney, a tomato salad and coriander yoghurt for an Indian inspired version.
